urdu transliteration text:
nanhey asgar ko amma ney kitney pyaar se paala thaUskey damm se ghar mey hamaarey qushiyaa aur ujaala thaTeer galey mey lagtey hi baba ney usey sambhaala tha Asgar veeraani mey ghabraaya to kaun sambhaaleyga
My mother looked after Asghar with great care,
@HujjatELC

phool badan tha qaasim ka paamaal kiyaa Jo lashkar neyQoon se kardi ret pey qurbaani tehreer bahattar neyNauha kamaal ney likhkhaa unka aur padhaa hai safdar neyRahey salaamath maatamdaar ye meri daadi ki hai dua
the seventy two martyrs gave their sacrifice,
@HujjatELC
